commit.message:
test: folder facet edge cases, chunk embedding tests, CI reliability (#653, #696, R5) (#724)

* test: folder facet edge cases, chunk embedding tests, CI reliability

- Add 26 new tests for folder facet edge cases (#653):
  parse_facet_counts with deeply nested, UTF-8, missing, single-entry paths;
  build_filter_queries with empty, whitespace, quotes, CJK, Arabic, parens;
  solr_escape for nested paths, CJK, mixed special chars;
  normalize_book folder_path extraction and absence handling

- Add chunk embedding / semantic search tests (Retro R5):
  keyword vs kNN chunk exclusion invariant; kNN with folder filters;
  RRF deduplication by document ID; chunk dedup scenario with highlights

- Improve integration test reliability (#696):
  Increase Solr health check retries 10→15, timeout 5s→10s, start_period 30s→60s;
  Add SolrCloud CLUSTERSTATUS readiness polling (all replicas active);
  Increase Solr wait_for_url attempts to 90; workflow timeout 60→75 min;
  Add ADMIN_API_KEY fallback, E2E auth env vars, rate limit override

